  "description": "This individual presents as a human corpse preserved by the cavern’s dry cold, with light skin drawn tight over sharp bone. Gray eyes sit deep in hollow sockets, fixed in a stare that never softens, while black hair lies in brittle, uneven clumps along a sunken scalp. The jawline shows old fractures set wrong, and the mouth hangs with a permanent asymmetry that exposes worn teeth. Fingers are long and rigid, with darkened nails and knuckles thickened by repeated impact against stone.",
